{"text_id":189229,"tokens":["We"," report"," the"," discovery"," of"," a"," major"," flaring"," episode"," of"," an"," ul","tral","uminous"," X","-","ray"," source"," (","UL","X",")"," in"," the"," nearby"," galaxy"," NGC"," ","1","3","6","5","."," This"," unprecedented"," event"," was"," detected"," using"," data"," from"," the"," Neil"," Geh","rels"," Observatory"," Swift"," satellite","."," Our"," analysis"," shows"," a"," dramatic"," increase"," in"," the"," X","-","ray"," luminosity"," of"," the"," source"," by"," a"," factor"," of"," \u223c","3"," over"," a"," period"," of"," a"," few"," days","."," We"," interpret"," this"," behavior"," as"," the"," accretion"," disk"," undergoing"," a"," major"," disruption",","," likely"," triggered"," by"," the"," fallback"," of"," matter"," onto"," a"," super","massive"," black"," hole","."," Our"," observations"," reveal"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," violent"," accretion"," processes"," occurring"," in"," the"," nuclei"," of"," galaxies","."," The"," physical"," mechanisms"," responsible"," for"," these"," outbursts"," remain"," debated",","," but"," our"," results"," suggest"," a"," connection"," between"," UL","X"," flares"," and"," the"," triggering"," of"," star"," formation"," activity"," in"," host"," galaxies","."," Our"," study"," emphasizes"," the"," importance"," of"," regular"," monitoring"," of"," UL","Xs"," for"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," the"," feedback"," mechanisms"," that"," regulate"," the"," activity"," of"," super","massive"," black"," holes","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}